reviewText: This film inspired me and many of my classmates when it was shown in class.  There are many landscape architects to emulate and most of these are practicing in the Western States ;)

We were fortunate enough to go to see a private screening of this documentary film earlier today.  it is a truly inspiring and wonderful production, documenting not just the great work that has been achieved by these women, but to find out more about the passion that they bring to their work.  Thank you ladies!
